title: Kelly Center for Hunger Relief Food Pantry
shortSummary: Kelly’s Food Pantry is the central El Paso food distribution center for the El Pasoans Fighting Hunger Food Bank. We’re proud to receive the majority of our food pantry’s resources each day from the food bank, and are extremely grateful for their partnership in fighting hunger in our community.

title: Amistad Elder Transport
shortSummary: Amistad provides transportation services to elderly and persons with disabilities to doctor’s appointments, cancer treatment centers, therapy, dialysis, pharmacies, employment, education centers, groceries stores, shopping centers and other approved destinations.

title: Project Vida Clinics
shortSummary: Project Vida Health Center clinics support the health and well-being of patients in all stages of life, for all ages. We offer a full range of primary health care services at multiple locations throughout El Paso and Hudspeth Counties.

title: Family Service of El Paso
shortSummary: The mission of Family Service of El Paso is to deliver mental health services that improve the life, health, and wellbeing of individuals and families in the El Paso community. As the largest mental health service agency in El Paso, we uniquely suited to serve local clients from nearly every demographic.
